reviewText:
Love these movies
They are so great to watch
I enjoy them so much
Only bad part is, I wish they kept the same philo vance, but, still, the 30's 40's made the best movies, I love murder, mystery, intrigue, you'll enjoy this as well.

The movie is a good B movie.
I would give it 3 stars.
The copy is one of the worst I have ever seen on a DVD.
It was transfered from, what appears, to be an old vhs tape recordered in LP.
Will never buy any DVD's from this mfg. again.
